OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with patchy
OL,6,Fdrizzle in the west. Then a dry and
OL,7,Fwarm afternoon with bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells. Some rain possible in the
OL,9,Fsouthwest through the late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain spreads northeast
OL,12,Fthrough the evening, heavy for a time.
OL,13,FBecoming dry overnight with some clear
OL,14,Fspells in the east but staying cloudy
OL,15,Fin the southwest and over Southern
OL,16,FUplands.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy to start but
OL,19,Fthis breaking up through the morning.
OL,20,FStaying dry and warm with prolonged
OL,21,Fbright or sunny spells through the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
